{"tid":1988414,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"歐盟被指因北京施壓淡化對中國的疫情指控","createTime":"2020-04-25T07:49:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T08:33:03.000Z","uid":37554,"like":11,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"3dc9b068586a21b77fb3feee9cbb3fb4c55601bd","tid":1988414,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T07:49:15.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】多個傳媒報道，歐盟在中國壓力下，修改一份關於新冠病毒的報告，淡化有關中國就疫情散播不實資訊的內容。<br />\n<br />\n《紐約時報》及路透社引述外交消息人士指，涉事報告原訂於周二發表。內文提到中國在疫情中，持續在全球層面發動假訊息行動，以推卸疫情責任及改善北京形象。<br />\n但有傳媒披露內容後，中國外交部接觸歐盟官員說，歐盟如果發表報告，將令北京非常憤怒，嚴重影響雙方合作。<br />\n<br />\n歐盟其後暫停發表報告，延至周五才發布，但文中指中國進行假訊息活動的內容被刪除，其他相關內容則被放到報告結束部分。<br />\n歐盟否認受到北京施壓，說修訂是因應內部對報告內容有異議。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=388922\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D388922&d=5PHCsmqc8bXRSfVPwy6hKvGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=e9611e13\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D388922&h=e4ab0274\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=388922</a>"},{"pid":"ec446f1020c5cda13f2b0880ea5498d59d415503","tid":1988414,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T07:49:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0a042b38ada6c223ea304c93264fc20dedcc94ae","tid":1988414,"uid":183758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T07:50:12.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"1c3bb4d82120e88a9cd1a0d74e2493e571acc613","tid":1988414,"uid":60785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T07:50:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a9ef8dfbd72edc38a4872aa9148598c884df146f","tid":1988414,"uid":55955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T07:51:02.000Z","msg":"歐豬"},{"pid":"92580860cdce30efd2092231ab5a49a7fcfbd274","tid":1988414,"uid":183758,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25